extension.description:
Insert YouTube hosted videos in Joomla! contents. Do not forget to go to Plugin Manager and publish the plugin. Online help at http://www.latenight-coding.com/joomla-addons/qtube.html

	Syntax: {qtube vid:=xxx}
	or:	{qtube vid:=xxx w:=320 h:=267 c1:=00ff00 c2:=0000ff b:=1 rel:=1 ap:=1 cl:=class id:=id}
